data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED!!! Beautiful Spanish Estate on 1.09 acre corner lot with 2 detached apartments with immediate income! The main 3 bedroom/ 2.5 bathroom home features updated electrical, electric car charger, AC (replaced in 2019), roof (replaced 2020), windows (replaced 2017), exterior painted in 2022, beautiful original wood floors throughout, French doors that lead into the separate office area, large bedrooms, newly remodeled laundry room which leads to the wood privacy fenced in backyard. The Master Bedroom has a sitting area with ample amount of light.  The 2 apartments which are accessible by a separate entrance. The 1st floor apartment (1 bedroom/1 bath) features a large living room/ dining combo, bathroom, large bedroom and is all ADA Accessible all recently updated. The 2nd Apartment (2 bedrooms/ 1 bathroom) is upstairs and features two bedrooms, kitchen, bathroom and living area. HOME HAS A VA LOAN THAT IS ASSUMABLE AT 2.99%APR WITH APPROVAL. Within minutes from Stetson University, restaurants and shopping!
